      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated Vanos system. Power delivery is linear and crisp, managed by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The rear subframe\u2014a critical structural area\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers, offering excellent turn-in response and damping. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina typical of a driven machine, the mechanical integrity is paramount, making this a perfect driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize performance and drivetrain health.",
      "price": 34500.0,
