      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is intact with only slight creasing on the driver's bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the ice-cold air conditioning and the responsive infotainment system. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection already completed. The engine pulls cleanly through the gears, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the suspension absorbs road imperfections without any unusual noises. With plenty of life left in the tires and brakes, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
